### Test: $lookup valid code "ebm"
# Expected: FHIR $lookup returns empty bundle (Aidbox does not implement $lookup)
# RESULT: FAIL — returns {"total":0,"entry":[]} instead of Parameters
GET http://localhost:8080/fhir/CodeSystem/$lookup?system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/CodeSystem/billing-type&code=ebm
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

